WEBVTT

00:02:56.920 --> 00:03:01.176
I left all work and gave
my all to the happiness of my family.

00:03:01.200 --> 00:03:03.896
But instead of being happy,

00:03:03.920 --> 00:03:10.920
slowly the belief that I could do
something in life started dying inside me.

00:03:11.480 --> 00:03:15.400
I eventually went into serious
clinical depression.

00:03:16.200 --> 00:03:18.216
I gave birth to two daughters.

00:03:18.240 --> 00:03:21.896
It was the happiest
occasion for my family,

00:03:21.920 --> 00:03:25.656
but that was the toughest
phase in my life.

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:28.976
I always wanted to be a good mother,

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:36.320
but when the time came I was completely
incapable of even looking after them.